    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Added a new command (Rangecommandnormal) which allows for a normal-mode command to be executed on the ranges. Also added mappings to quickly enter the Rangecommand and Rangecommandnormal command-lines. Added error-checking in case there are no ranges currently selected when the commands are executed.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="rowodd" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=1058">multipleRanges.vim</a></td>
