    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Removed the unique keyword from the internal script mappings as Vikas Agnihotri pointed out that this was causing a problem with potential reloading of the script while not adding anything to the ease of use.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=1055">multipleRanges.vim</a></td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><b>1.6</b></td>
